58.0	The_Silence_of_the_Lambs_(film)	The Silence of the Lambs (film)	The Silence of the Lambs is a 1991 American thriller film that blends elements of the crime and horror genres. It was directed by Jonathan Demme and stars Jodie Foster, Anthony Hopkins, Ted Levine, and Scott Glenn. It is based on the novel of the same name by Thomas Harris, his second to feature Hannibal Lecter, a brilliant psychiatrist and cannibalistic serial killer.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/8/86/The_Silence_of_the_Lambs_poster.jpg/220px-The_Silence_of_the_Lambs_poster.jpg
